column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release May 2016 Software v.2.6.1
Nutrient data for: 45001404, MILLVILLE, CINNAMON CRUNCH SQUARES, WHEAT & RICE CEREAL, UPC: 041498134914

WHOLE GRAIN WHEAT, SUGAR, RICE FLOUR, CANOLA OIL AND/OR PARTIALLY HYDROGENATED SOYBEAN OIL, FRUCTOSE, MALTODEXTRIN, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF: DEXTROSE, SALT, CINNAMON, SOY LECITHIN, TRISODIUM PHOSPHATE, ANNATTO AND CARAMEL COLOR, NATURAL FLAVOR. BHT (TO PRESERVE FRESHNESS). VITAMINS & MINERALS: VITAMIN B1 (THIAMIN MONONITRATE), VITAMIN B2 (RIBOFLAVIN), NIACIN (NIACINAMIDE), VITAMIN B6 (PYRIDOXINE HYDROCHLORIDE), FOLIC ACID, VITAMIN B12, VITAMIN A PALMITATE, VITAMIN C (SODIUM ASCORBATE), VITAMIN D, REDUCED IRON, ZINC (ZINC OXIDE), CALCIUM CARBONATE.
